@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Login (admin seed)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "leonan@fullcycle.com.br",
  "password": "123"
}

### Checkout - sucesso (novo usuário)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/checkout
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userName": "Guilherme",
  "email": "gui@fullcycle.com.br",
  "password": "senhaforte",
  "courseId": 2,
  "cardNumber": "4111222233334444"
}

### Checkout - pagamento recusado
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/checkout
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userName": "João",
  "email": "joao@teste.com",
  "password": "senhaforte",
  "courseId": 1,
  "cardNumber": "5111222233334444"
